{
  "stem": "14190.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And knowing-- knowing that-- she didn't know that they were going to be shot.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But she had a feeling that it's not going to be any good.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And perhaps here he'll have a chance to survive this way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "If he would be going with her, then for sure he wouldn't survive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So-- as it was, this couple, that had-- was childless couple.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They took him for their own.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he remained there for the-- for the-- for quite some time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And my mother-- my mother watched him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "She was-- she joined the partisans later, when she was shot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "She was wounded in Ponary and dug herself-- but not killed, as quite a few other people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "She dug herself from under the bodies and found a refuge in a nearby village.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And-- and then-- and then she joined the partisans, hoping that maybe she will find my father.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "My father didn't know all-- all about this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So and from far away, she from time to time, she watched my brother grow with this couple.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "She would-- she would come back and-- and watch.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And so when the war was ended, she tried to get him out of-- she tried to get him back.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And it was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "There was-- there was a court of law.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And then they presented all documents.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And she didn't have anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "She just knew that that was her child, and she wanted him back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this-- this Officer Blumkin, who was in-- very high in Russian Army and intelligence, I think, he told my-- my-- my mother, Mina, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You're going to get your son.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Even if you lose the-- because that would be by then the third time that they were trying to-- she was trying to get him.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
